            <section id="regression-line" class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12 items-center bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#004AAD] mb-4">The Line of Best Fit: Regression</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">When a linear correlation exists, we can draw a single straight line through the data that best represents the trend. This is called the **Least Squares Regression Line**. It's calculated to minimize the total distance from the line to all the data points, making it a powerful tool for prediction.</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">The most common regression line predicts the value of a dependent variable (Y) based on an independent variable (X), following the familiar equation $Y = aX + b$.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                     <div class="chart-container h-80 md:h-96">
                        <canvas id="regressionLineChart"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="normal-equations" class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#004AAD] mb-4 text-center">How to Calculate the Line</h2>
                <p class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">The regression line isn't just an estimate; it's determined precisely by solving a pair of "normal equations." These equations use sums of your data to find the exact values for the slope ($a$) and intercept ($b$) of the line. The choice of equations depends on which variable you are trying to predict.</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                    <div class="flow-box">
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-[#0079FF]">Predicting Y from X</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Use this when Y is your dependent variable.</p>
                        <div class="flow-arrow">â†“</div>
                        <div class="flow-box bg-blue-50">
                            <p class="font-mono font-semibold">Î£Y = aÎ£X + nb</p>
                            <p class="font-mono font-semibold">Î£XY = aÎ£XÂ² + bÎ£X</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flow-arrow">â†“</div>
                        <div class="flow-box bg-[#A1D6FF]">
                            <p class="font-bold text-lg text-black">Y = aX + b</p>
