                    <div class="flow-box">
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-[#0079FF]">Predicting X from Y</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Use this when X is your dependent variable.</p>
                        <div class="flow-arrow">â†“</div>
                         <div class="flow-box bg-blue-50">
                            <p class="font-mono font-semibold">Î£X = aÎ£Y + nb</p>
